<section xml:id="_md__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md6">
<title>🧠 Hovedidé &amp; gameplay</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Spillet genererer en hemmelig rækkefølge af farver (længde og forsøg er konfigurerbart via <computeroutput>Options</computeroutput>). <?linebreak?></para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Spilleren gætter kombinationer indenfor et maks. antal forsøg.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Feedback gives med <emphasis role="bold">sorte</emphasis> (rigtig farve på rigtig plads) og <emphasis role="bold">hvide</emphasis> (rigtig farve, forkert plads) markeringer.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para>Resultater gemmes og kan aflæses i <emphasis role="bold">Statistik</emphasis> (WPF) og via konsol.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>

<para><informaltable frame='bottom'><tgroup cols='1'><colspec align='center'/><tbody><row><entry align='center'>
</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></informaltable>
</para>
</section>
<section xml:id="_md__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md8">
<title>🧩 Arkitektur &amp; kode</title><section xml:id="_md__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md9">
<title>Core (Mastermind.Core)</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Domain</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>Farver</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Options</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Feedback</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Respons</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>GameResultater</computeroutput> – de centrale domænemodeller.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Services</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>SecretGenerator</computeroutput> (genererer hemmelig kombination), <computeroutput>Input</computeroutput> (validerer/parsing), <computeroutput>Evaluering</computeroutput> (beregner sort/hvid feedback).</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Persistence</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>OptionsRepository</computeroutput> gemmer/loader <computeroutput>Options</computeroutput> til/fra <computeroutput>Database/Options.json</computeroutput>. <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>JsonStatistikStore</computeroutput> implementerer <computeroutput>IStatistikStore</computeroutput> og gemmer resultater i <computeroutput>Database/Statistik.json</computeroutput>. <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>JsonFilePaths</computeroutput> sørger for mappe/sti-opsætning og <computeroutput>EnsureDir()</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Utils</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>StatistikTilføjer</computeroutput> – hjælpefunktioner ifm. statistik.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
<section xml:id="_md__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md10">
<title>WPF (Mastermind.Wpf)</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">MVVM</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>MainViewModel</computeroutput> (INotifyPropertyChanged) holder <computeroutput>CurrentView</computeroutput> og eksponerer kommandoer: <computeroutput>NytSpilCmd</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>OptionsCmd</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>StatistikCmd</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>ExitCmd</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Navigation</emphasis> <?linebreak?> Skifter mellem <computeroutput>Views/GameView</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Views/OptionsView</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Views/StatistikView</computeroutput> og afslutter via <computeroutput>ExitCmd</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">RelayCommand</emphasis> <?linebreak?> Let ICommand-implementering til bindinger.</para>
</listitem><listitem>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Lokalisering</emphasis> <?linebreak?> <computeroutput>Resources/Strings.da.xaml</computeroutput> og <computeroutput>Strings.en.xaml</computeroutput> muliggør dansk/engelsk tekst i UI.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</section>
<section xml:id="_md__r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md11">
<title>Konsol (Mastermind.Console)</title>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para><computeroutput>Program.cs</computeroutput> opretter <computeroutput>Options</computeroutput> (fx <computeroutput>længde: 3, maxForsøg: 9, showEmojis: true, sprog: Sprog.En</computeroutput>) samt <computeroutput>SecretGenerator</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Input</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Evaluering</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>KonsolMenu</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>Statistik</computeroutput>, <computeroutput>JsonStatistikStore</computeroutput> og starter <computeroutput>Spilstyring</computeroutput>.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>

<para><informaltable frame='bottom'><tgroup cols='1'><colspec align='center'/><tbody><row><entry align='center'>
</entry></row></tbody></tgroup></informaltable>
</para>
</section>
</section>
